                <td valign="top" class="row2"> <span class="smalltext"><b></b></span>
                  <p><span class="largetext">/salute
<br />

<br />
&lt;silent moment&gt;
<br />

<br />
I've said to many people, "It's your game, have fun", not only is the nail hitting the head, it places a point of focus on how and what we do here. There's a reason i still go into places like unrest or crushbone from time to time. and, it is for the fun, the stories, and the friends i may make. it relieves me to see a statement like this. to know that i'm not crazy for seeing the game as a place to do some cool things other than planar progression and getting the biggest toys. i couldn't forget anyone of u, and even though i get the strangest looks of "what the hell u talkin bout???" from all i talk to about u, i don't care because i was there, u were there, and we had a blast. 
<br />
well, b4 i get any mushier, i'm loggin in to nuke stuff...we all know my high personal quotas, and numbers have to be met <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
/kneel
<br />

