                  <p><span class="largetext">Well difinitely playing to have fun is difinitely the main goal here. I've stopped having fun in this game months ago but i play still for some dumb odd reason or another. yes i DO log off if i see only 2 ppl that i know on in guild or on my friends list. i mean whats the point? i play this game to have fun, not play with some random stangers day in and day out for some imaginary power. What made this game fun is the ppl i have met, made friends with and made memories with. Not the headaches, or the whining or its my job to make sure everyone is frickin happy or plan your raid and help u with your epic. I do it out of loyality and friendship. Not to be used as a stepping ladder.
