                <td valign="top" class="row2"> <span class="smalltext"><b></b></span>
                  <p><span class="largetext">Well, I guess we just all need to agree to disagree.  I interpreted Suvim's post one way and others have interpreted it other ways.  I took Mar's post as a personal attack that I needed to respond to because she generalized and said everyone who left the guild for those reasons.  I did leave for those reasons, but not those reasons alone.  I left KoA for reasons which I have explained to many of you over and over yet some still feel I left only "to be uber".  So be it.  I think the most important part of the post was that you should play with your friends...I always have and always will.  If I happen to get "uber" in the process...YaY me!  If I don't, hey...I'm still playing with my friends and enjoying the game I pay for.<br />_________________<br />~Tibi~
<br />
65 Shammie        <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=852077" target="_blank" class="postlink">Tibi's Stuff</a></span><span class="smalltext"></span></p>
